title: "The Slingshot: An AI Startup Simulation"
message: >-
  If you use this software in teaching or research, please cite it
  using the metadata from this file.
type: software
authors:
  - given-names: Ammon
    family-names: Salter
    orcid: 'https://orcid.org/0000-0002-4314-4090'
    affiliation: Warwick Business School, University of Warwick
  - given-names: Stefano
