repository-code: 'https://github.com/ammonsalter-del/The-Slingshot-Simulation'
url: 'https://slingshotsim.org'
abstract: >-
  An interactive browser-based business simulation for teaching
  entrepreneurship and innovation management. Players run an AI
  startup through sixteen quarters of strategic decisions —
  funding, hiring, competition, market opportunities, milestones
  and pivots — learning to make consequential decisions under
  uncertainty through experience, failure and replay.
keywords:
  - entrepreneurship
  - business simulation
  - serious games
  - innovation management
  - AI startups
  - teaching
  - educational games
  - decision-making under uncertainty
